T1  - Fairly Priced Deposit Insurance and Bank Charter Policy
AU  - CRAINE, ROGER
Y1  - 1995/12/01
PY  - 1995
DA  - 1995/12/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1540-6261.1995.tb05195.x
